doc.after: Cathay Pacific's head office, Cathay Pacific City, is located at Hong Kong International Airport, although the airline's registered office is on the 33rd floor of One Pacific Place.[51][52] Cathay Pacific City was scheduled to be built in increments between April and September 1998.[53] The headquarters opened in 1998.[54] Previously the airline's headquarters were at the Swire House, which was a complex in Central named after the airline's parent company.[55]
